radiographic_examinations.findings: Mild dependent atelectasis in the bilateral lung bases, no pleural or pericardial effusion. Multiple simple hepatic cysts bilaterally. Distended appendix with fluid, hyperenhancing wall, and an obstructing appendicolith. No periappendiceal fluid collection or intraperitoneal free air. Fat containing umbilical hernia and a ventral fat containing hernia just inferior to the umbilicus.
